dc_title_s: Bike Bridges City of Madison, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents bike bridges for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2020. [Existing and Planned Bicycle Bridge, Overpass, or Underpass. This data layer is used by the Dane County Bicycle Map and Neighborhood Development Plan Resource Viewer applications.]
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/
